@startuml Inquiry Submission - Sequence Diagram

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #667eea
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #f8f9ff
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #764ba2

title Client Inquiry & Notification Flow

actor "Client" as C
participant "Portfolio UI" as UI
participant "Inquiry\nController" as IC
participant "Validation\nLayer" as VL
participant "MongoDB" as DB
participant "Email\nService" as ES
participant "Shivam's Phone" as SP

== FORM SUBMISSION ==

C -> UI: Fills "Hire Me" Form
note right: Name, Email, Budget, Message
activate UI

C -> UI: Clicks "Send Proposal"
UI -> VL: Client-Side Validation
VL --> UI: Valid ✓

UI -> IC: POST /api/inquiry/new
activate IC

IC -> VL: Server-Side Validation (Sanitize)
activate VL
VL --> IC: Safe Data ✓
deactivate VL

IC -> DB: Create Inquiry Document
activate DB
DB --> IC: Inquiry ID: #9921
deactivate DB

== NOTIFICATION SYSTEM ==

par Notify Client
  IC -> ES: sendAutoReply(clientEmail)
  activate ES
  ES -> ES: Render HTML Template
  ES -> C: Email: "Received! I'll reply in 24h"
  deactivate ES
end

par Notify Shivam (URGENT)
  IC -> ES: sendAdminAlert(details)
  activate ES
  ES -> SP: Email: "New Lead: $500 Budget"
  deactivate ES
end

== RESPONSE ==

IC --> UI: 201 Created
deactivate IC

UI -> UI: Show Success Animation
UI --> C: "Message Sent Successfully"
deactivate UI

@enduml